data.description: Truly Amazing hidden Gem in Hickory Ridge!  Spacious 3 bedroom, 3 full bathroom cozy open layout home with many updates through out.  Recently fully renovated with hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings, granite countertops, beautiful white cabinets and more. Fully finished walk out basement with full bathroom.  Brand new water just installed last month. Home has two sheds in backyard, gutter guards and spacious wrap around deck with fully fenced in yard.
